Titolo: The 4th Coming

Anno: 1999

Descrizione: The 4th Coming (abbreviated T4C), and also known in French as La Quatrième Prophétie, is a massively multiplayer online role-playing game (MMORPG) originally produced by Vircom Interactive for Windows-based operating systems. Vircom opened the first server for testing before releasing server licenses. There are no known release notes for versions prior to the release of version 1.0. The 4th Coming was later purchased by Dialsoft, who sells server licenses and continues to develop the game under the official project name of T4C Next Chapter.

Genere: Action role-playing game

Valutazione: N/A
